睇嘅戲會自己一條友睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近一次自己睇你的名字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4e6de3bc64d682e342339ff1a5f3daa6d0bd60","tid":57052,"uid":67626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:07:36.000Z","msg":"成撚日自己去睇戲<br />\n仲要平視線坐中間位<br />\n<br />\n利申  毒L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc4772743f59b1c2bc1b0298ee4b9e13984c78c","tid":57052,"uid":36829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:14:28.000Z","msg":"真係鐘意套戲既都會照一個人入去睇既，以前ex陪我睇過頭幾輯marvel角色 d戲，但散左要自己一個睇續集，次次上映都仲會心存希望循例問下佢一唔一齊睇，但結果次次都係藍剔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be49f938fd62bc68c3c8d3c2a55780713333949","tid":57052,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:19:51.000Z","msg":"自己一個睇都唔差架"},{"pid":"f7cb1aa93f5386379705a64e8404e33e5b0dc2c8","tid":57052,"uid":42048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:22:32.000Z","msg":"以前嘅我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n散左之後冇睇過戲，直到同現任開始拍拖"},{"pid":"5e14f4c9ad99c495522d8af0528bbb6dd12bc830","tid":57052,"uid":36663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而記唔起上次幾時同人一齊睇戲 自己入戲院一定熄電話同絕少食嘢 同其他人睇好驚佢哋會想講嘢/睇電話/食嘢食得好大聲 又唔想兜口兜面話佢哋(以前經驗) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4223c3b37a642fe41339aa4200c63c840c62c72","tid":57052,"uid":67942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍拖個陣兩年睇左60套戲 <br />\n分左手年幾只睇過3套</blockquote><br />\nsame"}]}